action_item: Appointment Types - Work with DoctorCloud team to define specific appointment types for STI, including express testing.
notes: Appointment types must be detailed beyond general categories to facilitate reporting.

action_item: Reports - Send a list of required data points for reports to the team.
notes: Ensure all necessary data points for reporting are captured.

action_item: Service Codes - Clarify functionality of payments and service codes with DoctorCloud team.
notes: Determine how payments are logged and if they can be locked to specific services.

action_item: Users & Roles - Confirm if multiple sliding fee scales can be accommodated in the system.
notes: Ensure the system can handle different sliding fee scales for various programs.

action_item: Data Migration - Provide a list of 'My Phrases' used in the current system for migration to the new system.
notes: These phrases are essential for maintaining workflow efficiency in the new system.
